### Register/Signup New User - Alice
POST http://localhost:8082/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "fullName": "Alice Johnson"
}

###

### Register/Signup New User - Bob
POST http://localhost:8082/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bob",
  "password": "securepass456",
  "email": "bob@example.com",
  "fullName": "Bob Smith"
}

###

### Login as Alice
POST http://localhost:8082/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "alice",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Login as Bob
POST http://localhost:8082/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "bob",
  "password": "securepass456"
}

###

### Try Invalid Signup - Existing Email
POST http://localhost:8082/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "charlie",
  "password": "password789",
  "email": "alice@example.com",
  "fullName": "Charlie Brown"
}

###

### Try Invalid Signup - Weak Password
POST http://localhost:8082/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "david",
  "password": "weak",
  "email": "david@example.com",
  "fullName": "David Wilson"
}

###

### Get Total Users Count
GET http://localhost:8082/auth/users/count

###

### Get All Messages
GET http://localhost:8082/api/messages

###

### Get Messages from Alice
GET http://localhost:8082/api/messages/sender/alice

###

### Get Messages from Bob
GET http://localhost:8082/api/messages/sender/bob

###

### View H2 Database Console (open in browser)
GET http://localhost:8082/h2-console
# Username: sa
# Password: (leave blank)
# JDBC URL: jdbc:h2:mem:chatdb

###

